  "text": "Ministry of Finance (Department of Revenue) (CENTRAL ECONOMIC INTELLIGENCE BUREAU) (COFEPOSA UNIT) ORDER New Delhi, the 13th January, 2005 In exercise of the powers conferred by sub-section (1) of Section 3 of the Conservation of Foreign Exchange and Prevention of Smuggling Activities Act, 1974 (52 of 1974), the Central Government hereby specially empowers Shri Kishan Singh Joint Secretary to the government of India, for the purpose of the said Section. [F.No. 671/18/2001-Cus.VIII] N.M. Krishnan Dy. Secy. -- 1 of 1 --",
